<template>
  <form @submit.prevent="fnSubmitHandler">
    <input
      type="text"
      v-model="todo"
      placeholder="type new todo-list"
    />
    <button>click</button>
  </form>
</template>

<script>
import { ref } from 'vue';
export default {
  setup() {

    return {
      todo,

};
